# 🚗🚌 College Bus vs Car Classifier using CNN

A deep learning-based image classification project that identifies whether a vehicle is a College Bus or a Car using Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN). This project also includes advanced features such as image upload prediction, campus vehicle monitoring, and a vehicle counting system.

# 📌 Project Overview

This project is designed to automate vehicle identification inside a college campus using Artificial Intelligence and Deep Learning techniques. The model is trained using CNN architecture to classify images accurately between buses and cars.

The system can be used for:

Campus vehicle monitoring
Smart parking systems
Traffic management
Automatic vehicle classification
CCTV-based vehicle counting
# 🎯 Features

✔️ Vehicle Image Classification
✔️ College Bus vs Car Detection
✔️ CNN-Based Deep Learning Model
✔️ Image Upload Prediction System
✔️ Real-Time Prediction Support
✔️ Vehicle Counting Feature
✔️ Data Augmentation for Better Accuracy
✔️ Dropout & Early Stopping to Reduce Overfitting
✔️ User-Friendly Interface

