🏗️ Model Architecture

The CNN model includes:

Convolution Layers
MaxPooling Layers
Dropout Layers
Dense Layers
ReLU Activation Function
Sigmoid Activation Function

These layers help the model learn image patterns effectively and improve prediction accuracy.

# 📈 Accuracy Improvement Techniques

To improve model performance, the following techniques were used:

Data Augmentation
Dropout Regularization
Early Stopping
Image Rescaling
Transfer Learning (Optional)
🚀 How to Run the Project
1️⃣ Install Required Libraries
pip install -r requirements.txt
2️⃣ Run Training File
python train.py
3️⃣ Run Streamlit App
streamlit run app.py
🖼️ Prediction System

The user can upload a vehicle image, and the model predicts whether the image belongs to:

🚌 College Bus
🚗 Car

with prediction confidence.

